name: 2013 Pearl Wrap- Tahitian
description: pearl. love. & Rockabella Jewels style three. style no. PLROC3. 1 x 9-11 mm Tahitian pearl, color varies; Collaboration with Pearl.Love. Jewelry. how to wear pearl wrap bracelets ... center pearl on wrist and wrap both ends around as many times as possible. the bracelet wraps three times on the average woman’s wrist. tie two knots to secure the bracelet. leave remaining silk cord hanging or trim off extra cord at each end. be sure to either trim just past an existing knot or tie a new knot just inside of where you are going to cut. this will eliminate fraying of the silk cord at the closure point and will make removing the bracelet and putting it back on much easier. bracelet can be worn in water; color may fade over time if repeatedly worn in water and sun. can also be worn as a necklace or anklet; follow guidance above.
